        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 8. Ophiopsila xmasilluminans new species (Holotype, WAM Z99800), SEM photographs of internal ossicles of arm at distal portion of the arm. A, vertebra, lateral view; B–D, lateral arm plates, external view (B), internal view, an arrowhead indicates a perforation (C) and distal view (D); E, F, ventral arm plates, internal (E) and external (F) views; G, arm spine; H, tentacle scale; I, dorsal arm plate. Arrowheads indicate orientations: ba, basal side; dis, distal side; ex, external side; pro, proximal side. Abbreviations: DT, depression for tentacle; LF, longitudinal furrow." ;
